quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  44,17,"Ndipo, ndithudi, tidawayesa anthu a Farawo, iwo asanabadwe, ndipo kudadza kwa iwo Mtumwi wolemekezeka"
  44,18,Naati “Bweretsani kwa ine akapolo a Mulungu.” “Ndithudi ine ndine Mtumwi wokhulupirika kwa inu.”
  44,19,“Ndipo musachitire mwano Mulungu. Ndithudi ine ndadza kwa inu ndi ulamuliro wooneka.”
  44,20,“Ndipo ndithudi ine ndapempha chitetezo cha Ambuye wanga ndi Ambuye wanu kuti musandiononge.”
  44,21,"“Koma ngati inu simundikhulupirira ine, ndiye mundisiye ndekha.”"
  44,22,"Ndipo iye anati kwa Ambuye wake, “Anthu awa ndi ochimwa.”"
  44,23,Choka iwe ndi akapolo anga nthawi yausiku. Ndithudi iwe udzalondoledwa
  44,24,“Ileke nyanja kukhala monga mmene ili. Ndithudi iwo ndi anthu amene adzamizidwa.”
  44,25,Kodi ndi minda ingati ndiponso a kasupe angati amene iwo adasiya
  44,26,Ndi minda ya chimanga ndi malo olemekezeka
  44,27,Ndi zinthu zabwino zimene amasangalala nazo
  44,28,Kotero zinali choncho. Ndipo Ife tidawasankha anthu ena kuti atenge zinthu zawo
  44,29,Kumwamba kapena dziko lapansi silidakhetse msozi chifukwa cha iwo ndipo iwo sadapatsidwe mpumulo
  44,30,Ndithudi tidapulumutsa ana a Israyeli ku chilango chochititsa manyazi
  44,31,Chimene chidaperekedwa ndi Farawo. Ndithudi iye adali wamwano ndi mmodzi wa anthu oswa malamulo
  44,32,Ndithudi tidawasankha iwo kuti akhale ndi nzeru kuposa mitundu ina
  44,33,Ndipo tidawapatsa chivumbulutso chimene chidali ndi mayesero ooneka
  44,34,Ndithudi iwo akuti
  44,35,“Palibe china chilichonse kupatula imfa yathu yoyamba ndipo ife sitidzaukitsidwa kwa akufa.”
  44,36,“Kotero bweretsa makolo athu ngati zimene ukunena ndi zoona!”
  44,37,Kodi awa ndi opambana kuposa anthu a Tubba ndi iwo amene adalipo kale? Ife tidawaononga onse ndipo iwo adali olakwa
  44,38,Ndipo ife sitidalenge kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili m’menemo mwamasewera
  44,39,Ife sitidazilenge zonsezi kupatula mwachoonadi ndipo ambiri a iwo sadziwa
  44,40,Ndithudi tsiku lachimaliziro ndi tsiku lomaliza kwa iwo onse
  44,41,Ndi tsiku limene bwenzi sadzakumbukira bwenzi ake ndipo sadzalandira chithandizo
  44,42,Kupatula yekhawo amene waonetsedwa chisomo cha Mulungu. Ndithudi Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha
  44,43,Ndithudi mtengo wa Zaqqum
  44,44,Udzakhala chakudya cha anthu ochimwa
  44,45,"Monga mafuta owira, chidzabwata m’mimba mwawo"
  44,46,Monga ngati madzi ogaduka
  44,47,“Mugwire iye ndipo mududuzireni m’kati mwa Gahena.”
  44,48,Ndipo thirani pamutu pake chilango cha madzi owira
  44,49,“Lawani ichi! Ndithudi inu munali amphamvu ndi aulemu.”
  44,50,“Ndithudi! Ichi ndicho chimene munali kukayika.”
  44,51,“Ndithudi! Iwo amene amalewa zoipa adzakhala kumalo otetezedwa.”
  44,52,Pakati pa minda ndi a kasupe
  44,53,"Iwo atavala Silika wokhuthala ndi wokongola, atakhala moyang’anizana"
  44,54,Kotero zidzakhala choncho ndipo Ife tidzawakwatitsa kwa akazi a maso aakuluakulu okongola
  44,55,Iwo adzaitanitsa chipatso cha mtundu uliwonse mwamtendere ndi mokhazikika
  44,56,Ndipo iwo sadzalawa imfa kupatula imfa yoyamba ndipo Iye adzawapulumutsa ku chilango chowawa cha Gahena
  44,57,Chisomo chochokera kwa Ambuye wako! Chimenechi chidzakhala chinthu chopambana kwambiri
  44,58,Ndithudi Ife taipanga Koraniyi kukhala yapafupi m’chiyankhulo chako ndi cholinga chakuti mwina angathe kukumbukira
  44,59,Kotero iwe dikira chifukwa nawonso ali kudikira
  45,1,Ha Mim
  45,2,"Chivumbulutso cha Buku ndi chochokera kwa Mulungu, Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini nzeru"
  45,3,Ndithudi kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi kuli zizindikiro kwa anthu okhulupirira
  45,4,M’chilengedwe chanu nyama zimapezeka paliponse pa dziko lapansi ndipo ndi zizindikiro kwa iwo amene ali okhulupirira kwenikweni
  45,5,"Ndi m’kasinthidwe ka usiku ndi usana ndi m’chakudya chimene amatumiza kuchokera ku mitambo ndipo amapereka moyo ku nthaka imene idali yakufa ndipo m’kasinthidwe ka mphepo, muli zizindikiro kwa anthu ozindikira"
  45,6,Ichi ndi chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Mulungu chimene tili kulakatula kwa iwe mwachoonadi. Nanga ndi uthenga uti wa Mulungu ndi chivumbulutso chake chiti chomwe iwo akhoza kukhulupirira
  45,7,Tsoka kwa wochimwa aliyense wabodza
  45,8,Amene amamva mawu a Mulungu amene ali kunenedwa kwa iye ndipo amapitirizabe kunyada ngati iye sanamve. Motero muuze iye za chilango chowawa
  45,9,"Ndipo pamene iye akamva mawu a Mulungu, amawasandutsa kukhala masewera. Ndipo kwa otere kudzakhala chilango chochititsa manyazi"
  45,10,"Kutsogolo kwawo kuli Gahena, ndipo sadzapeza phindu lina lililonse pa ntchito zawo kapenakwaiwoameneadawasandutsakukhalawowasamala poonjezera pa Mulungu. Ndipo iwo adzalandira chilango chowawa"
  45,11,"Ichi ndi chilangizo choona. Ndipo iwo amene amakana zizindikiro za Ambuye wawo, adzalandira chilango chapadera chowawa"